de.htw.berlin.polysun4diac.forte.datatypes

Enum ForteDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ForteDataType>
      • de.htw.berlin.polysun4diac.forte.datatypes.ForteDataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ForteDataType>

    public enum ForteDataType
extends java.lang.Enum<ForteDataType>
    Enum for the supported IEC 61499 data types that can be sent to/received from FORTE.

    The data type equivalents are listed in the following table:

    JAVA object/primitive IEC 61499 data type
    boolean BOOL
    int SINT, INT, DINT, USINT, UINT, UDINT
    long LINT, ULINT
    float REAL
    double LREAL
    DateAndTime*, LocalDateTime DATE_AND_TIME
    String STRING
    *DateAndTime is part of this library.

    Author:
    Marc Jakobi

    HTW Berlin

    July 2017
